                <head>No. 265.<lb/>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Blaine</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Morton</persName>
                    </hi>.</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1881-12-02">
                            <hi rend="italic">December</hi> 2, 1881</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Ascertain promptly, and advise by telegraph to-morrow, whether, and at what time
                    we may expect revocation of edict prohibiting importation of American pork.
                    Important.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>BLAINE.</signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
